description: Everybody knows that being a member of a Frat house is probably the coolest thing you can do while in college, but depends on how much are you willing to do to get accepted, is what separates the boys from the men. I guess these guys were willing to do anything to get in this frat. In the entire history of dickdorm submissions, we have never received footage with this kind of hazing. Pretty fucking amazing if you ask me. They were putting these boys through everything. From getting cover in flour, to showering together, to having a sword fight, to a blow job, to ass licking, to... well, you get the idea. If you dont, then watch the video and be amazed.
title: Get Gazed
